  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 36bccf2d2c1763242ba11eb36cdffde2, type: 3}
  m_Name: OasisGenLogProfile
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  pages:
  - text: '2097-05-21

      23:18


      This is probably the most important day
      of my life. I have finally managed to create the Farm Restorer prototype.

      If
      the world truly collapses in nuclear fire, this device will give people a chance.
      On scorched, radioactive wastelands it will be possible to create vast farms
      of radiation-resistant crops, places where everyone will have access to food
      and where the widespread hunger that may follow the war will no longer be a
      threat.


      I am only missing two elements: a power source and suitable
      seeds.

      The power source does not need to be complicated. After the war,
      car batteries will be everywhere, in the wrecks of abandoned vehicles. This
      is a perfect and easily accessible solution.'
  - text: "As for seeds, the best option would be modified wheat, resistant and fast-growing.
      I\u2019m sure it can be found somewhere. The grains just need to be placed
      in special containers \u2013 I have a few empty ones in the cabinet nearby,
      they fit perfectly with the device.\n\nFor now, I\u2019ll close my eyes. Tomorrow
      I\u2019ll ask one of the soldiers to go and fetch the seeds for me.\nAnd after
      that, we\u2019ll run the first test of my invention."
  actions:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: f4c2ca22ccdd854469d4493232e8f2b2, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 319959015c52c1a48b07ef9989b90b43, type: 2}
